# Step 6: Project Detail Page UI

**Phase:** 6, Step 6
**Status:** Not Started
**Depends on:** Step 1 (projects API -- `GET /api/projects/:id`), Step 2 (deployments API -- `POST /api/projects/:id/deployments`), Step 5 (StatusBadge component)
**Blocks:** Steps 7-8 (child pages rendered inside this layout)

---

## Goal

Build the project overview page and update the project layout with interactive tab navigation. The overview page shows the current production URL, the 5 most recent deployments with status and commit info, and quick action buttons (Deploy, View Logs). The layout fetches project data and passes context to child pages via React context or props.

