## Deploy Button Flow

```
User clicks "Deploy"
    |
    v
Confirmation dialog: "Deploy from main branch?"
    |
    +--> [Cancel] --> close dialog
    |
    +--> [Confirm]
           |
           v
         POST /api/projects/:id/deployments
         Body: {} (empty -- defaults to production branch)
           |
           +--> Success (201)
           |      |
           |      v
           |    Navigate to /projects/:id/deployments/:newDeploymentId
           |    Show success toast: "Deployment triggered"
           |
           +--> Error
                  |
                  v
                Show error toast: "Failed to trigger deployment"
```

**Deploy button states:**
- Default: gray/dark button "Deploy"
- Loading: disabled, spinner icon, "Deploying..."
- Success: brief green flash, then navigation

---

## Formatting Utilities

Add to `apps/dashboard/src/lib/format.ts`:

```typescript
export function formatCommitSha(sha: string | null): string {
  return sha ? sha.substring(0, 7) : "-------";
}

export function formatDuration(ms: number | null): string {
  if (ms === null) return "--";
  const seconds = Math.floor(ms / 1000);
  if (seconds < 60) return `${seconds}s`;
  const minutes = Math.floor(seconds / 60);
  const remainingSeconds = seconds % 60;
  return `${minutes}m ${remainingSeconds}s`;
}
```

