## Testing

### Visual Tests

1. **Tab navigation:** Clicking each tab navigates to the correct page. Active tab has border and dark text.
2. **Active tab detection:** Visiting `/projects/:id/deployments/abc123` highlights the "Deployments" tab.
3. **Production URL:** Displayed correctly, opens in new tab on click.
4. **No deployments:** "No production deployment yet" shown. View Logs button is disabled.
5. **Recent deployments:** Shows up to 5 deployments with correct status, commit, branch, time, and duration.
6. **Deploy button:** Shows confirmation dialog, triggers POST, navigates on success.
7. **Deploy error:** Error toast appears on API failure.
8. **Loading state:** Skeleton shows while project data loads.
9. **404 state:** Invalid project ID shows "Project not found" message.
10. **Deployment row click:** Clicking a deployment navigates to its detail page.
11. **"View all deployments" link:** Navigates to `/projects/:id/deployments`.
